stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_slot: state.slot % SLOTS_PER_EPOCH == 0
    q_check_slot --> q_check_epoch: slot is epoch boundary
    q_check_slot --> q_no_fork: slot is not epoch boundary
    q_check_epoch --> q_upgrade: compute_epoch_at_slot(state.slot) == FULU_FORK_EPOCH
    q_check_epoch --> q_no_fork: epoch != FULU_FORK_EPOCH
    q_upgrade --> [*]: upgrade_to_fulu(state)
    q_no_fork --> [*]: no state change
